    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/c6ffcd3ad189cc0b435b86dc4d2ce224.avif?t=1739005912\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set in the near future, the technology to reconstruct prehistoric life has just been discovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explosions ring out at the conference center, and as evacuees pour out of the complex, some show symptoms of a mysterious illness. Hours pass and contact is lost with first responders at the scene. Fearing a chemical or biological attack may be the cause, a CBRN detachment known as WYVERN Team is dispatched to perform search and rescue operations. Little do they know what primal terror awaits them there.    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/e8a575627a87d0a56674bc89738cf783.poster.avif?t=1739005912\" width=524 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/e8a575627a87d0a56674bc89738cf783.webm?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/e8a575627a87d0a56674bc89738cf783.mp4?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/09455382dd303dbccaea325c178b6649.avif?t=1739005912\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll face over a dozen different <i>formerly</i> extinct species in Paleophage. From bloodthirsty carnivorous dinosaurs to giant insects, you never know what might be lurking around the next corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Including, but not limited to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utahraptor</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ceratosaurus</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Styracosaurus</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spinosaurus</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arthropleura</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prestosuchus</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/5d8abea33833d4ba993c006495812bce.poster.avif?t=1739005912\" width=524 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/5d8abea33833d4ba993c006495812bce.webm?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/5d8abea33833d4ba993c006495812bce.mp4?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/65836e0913fc4a1062e6c1b722589f20.avif?t=1739005912\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight for survival through hotels, transit stations, parks, and more as you make your way through a major American Midwest city overrun by prehistoric beasts. Play as two different characters with unique arsenals in exciting over-the-shoulder third person survival horror gameplay. Featuring extras like additional unlockable game modes and collectible creature models.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >        <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/6d51cd0c3e9dcc88ff90105ebfbef568.poster.avif?t=1739005912\" width=524 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/6d51cd0c3e9dcc88ff90105ebfbef568.webm?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2198310/extras/6d51cd0c3e9dcc88ff90105ebfbef568.mp4?t=1739005912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
